response.overview: Introducing the Kettlebell which is particularly good at sculpting a slim waistline because the odd shape causes the weight to be distributed unevenly. Your core muscles are continuously engaged throughout every motion to control the bell’s shifting center of gravity!  ﻿Ready to get your sweat on with 20 minutes of Kettlebell Swings and AB exercises Train 3x a week to increase your core strength Warm Up and Cool Down included
response.tagline: A 20 minute guided core and cardio workout.
response.title: ABSolute ABS - Cardio & Abs
